reviews.review_text: Thanks! This is the same recording of tmy old cassette that I wore out many years ago!!What a wicked show-best china rider ever in my humble opinion-absolutely sets sail in the rider jam and one of the most heartfelt Believe It or Not's i've heard:-))Phil was really thumpin this night!Better sounding recordings i'm sure but I think this one captures the essence....
